Definition: someone who is so ardently devoted to something that it resembles an addiction
Example: a golf addict; a car nut; a bodybuilding freak; a news junkie
Synonyms: verb, consumption, nut, freak, junkie, junky, enthusiast, someone, who, is, so, ardently, devoted, to, something, that, it, resembles, an, addiction, a, golf, car, bodybuilding, news
Category: noun.person
